acme.validation.audit-report.start-before-end.message = Publication requires a logical time frame where both dates are set in the future
acme.validation.auditReport.startMoment.future = The start date cannot be in the past or present
acme.validation.auditReport.endMoment.future = The completion date must occur after the current time
acme.validation.audit-report.published-without-audit-section.message = At least one audit section is required to proceed with the publication

